# Deep Technical Audit

- [ ] DB Schema Review (Normalization, indexes, security)
- [ ] Backend API Review (REST, Auth, N+1 queries)
- [ ] Business Logic Review (Correctness, race conditions)
- [ ] Frontend Review (Components, state, renders)
